<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_c6c93895df0a.aspx"><b>石灰吟</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e6%98%8e%e4%bb%a3">明代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%ba%8e%e8%b0%a6">于谦</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonc6c93895df0a">
<p>千锤万凿出深山，烈火焚烧若等闲。<br />粉骨碎身全不怕，要留清白在人间。</p>
<p>(一作：千锤万击出深山 / 千鎚万击出深山)<br />(一作：粉骨碎身全不惜 / 粉身碎骨浑不怕 / 粉身碎骨全不怕)</p>
