<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_10086b1c2cc6.aspx"><b>书河上亭壁</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e5%af%87%e5%87%86">寇准</a></p>
