<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_84b5b3488790.aspx"><b>惠崇春江晚景二首 / 惠崇春江晓景二首</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e8%8b%8f%e8%bd%bc">苏轼</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson84b5b3488790">
<p>竹外桃花三两枝，春江水暖鸭先知。<br />蒌蒿满地芦芽短，正是河豚欲上时。</p>
<p>两两归鸿欲破群，依依还似北归人。<br />遥知朔漠多风雪，更待江南半月春。</p>
